com.brownian.morse.receivers

Class LatinReceiverAsync

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brownian.morse.receivers.LatinReceiver
      • com.brownian.morse.receivers.LatinReceiverAsync

  • public class LatinReceiverAsync
extends LatinReceiver
    A LatinReceiver that supports asynchronous operations. Instead of synchronously calling and waiting, these send methods return immediately, and notify a listener when the provided character has been consumed. Calling parent send() methods is equivalent to providing null for a listener.
